<D>__{well, it's authoritative and is overwhelmingly documented.}
<C>__{lowell}
<D>__{and it's bullshit. and if i'm right, are you going to put the journal 's reputation behind a story that's going to blow up in your face?}
<C>__{charlie phillips}
<D>__{i will take a look at what you got. but i'm not moving any deadlines 'cause you say so.}
